B%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Qu%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1-Thang-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-linh-t%C6%B0u-t%C3%A1c/poem-ZFALwW-Oh0NxiQJY2bUNPQ">Phụng đồng Quách cấp sự “Thang đông linh tưu tác” - 奉同郭給事湯東靈湫作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/S%C3%A0i-m%C3%B4n/poem-vg2174OhgSqPjoq6H1VPpg">Sài môn - 柴門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%C6%A1-ng%C5%A9-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tr%E1%BB%B1c-%C4%91oan-ng%E1%BB%8D-ti%E1%BA%BFt-t%E1%BB%83-sinh-vi-l%E1%BB%85-nh%C3%A2n-th%C3%A0nh-tam-lu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-_XkxoSAnG_cF5jYIbWxc2A">Sơ ngũ nhật trực đoan ngọ tiết tể sinh vi lễ, nhân thành tam luật kỳ 3 - 初五日直端午節宰牲為禮，因成三律其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C6%B0u-C%E1%BA%A3nh-V%C4%83n/poem-oAPFrVULwriLJKYpUb1DeA">Tặng Lưu Cảnh Văn - 贈劉景文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
